            <title><![CDATA[Dragon Age: The Veilguard Has A Mass Effect Easter Egg]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dragon-age-the-veilguard-has-a-mass-effect-easter-egg/1100-6527538/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
